    <title>cs50.lecture5-7</title>
    <url>/2024/08/04/cs50-5-10/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<hr>
<h1 id="lecture-5-Data-Structures"><a href="#lecture-5-Data-Structures" class="headerlink" title="lecture 5 Data Structures"></a>lecture 5 Data Structures</h1><p>首先来链表的模板</p>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">#include &lt;stdio.h&gt;</span><br><span class="line">#include &lt;stdlib.h&gt;</span><br><span class="line">typedef struct node</span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    int value;</span><br><span class="line">    struct node* next;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;node;</span><br><span class="line">int main()</span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    node* head=NULL;</span><br><span class="line">    int number;</span><br><span class="line">    do&#123;</span><br><span class="line">        scanf(&quot;%d&quot;,&amp;number);</span><br><span class="line">        if(number!=-1)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">            //add to linked-list</span><br><span class="line">            node*p =(node*)malloc(sizeof(node));//temp链表请求node结构的内存 包含value和下一个指针</span><br><span class="line">            p-&gt;value=number;</span><br><span class="line">            p-&gt;next=NULL;</span><br><span class="line">            node *last=head;//让一个名为last的链表成为head</span><br><span class="line">            //find the last</span><br><span class="line">            if(last)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">                while(last-&gt;next)//last 指的地址存在就下一个实现了遍历</span><br><span class="line">                &#123;</span><br><span class="line">                    last=last-&gt;next;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">                &#125;</span><br><span class="line">                last-&gt;next=p;</span><br><span class="line">            &#125;else&#123;</span><br><span class="line">                head=p;</span><br><span class="line">            &#125;</span><br><span class="line">            </span><br><span class="line">        &#125; </span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    &#125;while(number!=-1);//读到-1就停止</span><br><span class="line">    return 0;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>


	<div class="row">
    <embed src="/file/cs50-5.pdf" width="100%" height="550" type="application/pdf">
	</div>




<hr>
<h1 id="lecture-6-python"><a href="#lecture-6-python" class="headerlink" title="lecture 6 python"></a>lecture 6 python</h1><p><strong><strong>python</strong> Object Oriented Programming 简称为OOP</strong><br>本节课大多数介绍了python与c的不同和python的优势<br>os：你py真还是nb的 同时学了c和py可以强烈感受到c和py底层建筑和瑞士军刀实际运用的利弊</p>
<h2 id="面向对象"><a href="#面向对象" class="headerlink" title="面向对象"></a>面向对象</h2><p>面向对象就是将问题分解成一个一个步骤，对每个步骤进行相应的抽象，形成对象，通过不同对象之间的调用，组合解决问题。</p>
<h2 id="面向过程"><a href="#面向过程" class="headerlink" title="面向过程"></a>面向过程</h2><p>面向过程是一种自顶而下的编程模式。把问题分解成一个一个步骤，每个步骤用函数实现，依次调用即可。</p>
<h2 id="区别"><a href="#区别" class="headerlink" title="区别"></a>区别</h2><ul>
<li>py可能运行会比c慢 占用内存更多 因为py可以帮你<strong>管理内存</strong></li>
<li>具有丰富的库生态系统 没有标准的头文件</li>
<li>没有分号 不用声明变量类型</li>
<li>get-string函数在py中 收益效益没这么高了 因为input（）函数</li>
<li><strong>缩进尤为重要</strong></li>
<li>py不用担心整形数溢出（超出限度变成0）但是浮点数的精确度一直存在</li>
<li>可以线性搜索 不用像c一样遍历数组</li>
<li>用sys库可以做像c的事情 但是访问方式不一样<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">import sys</span><br><span class="line">if len(sys.argv)!=2:</span><br><span class="line">        print(&quot;missing command-line argument&quot;)</span><br><span class="line">        sys.exit(1)</span><br><span class="line">print (f&quot;hello,&#123;sys.argv[1]&#125;&quot;)</span><br><span class="line">sys.exit(0)//可以用你想要的方式退出</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li>
</ul>
<h3 id="其他语法"><a href="#其他语法" class="headerlink" title="其他语法"></a>其他语法</h3><ul>
<li>for + else</li>
<li>exception:<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">while Ture:</span><br><span class="line">        try:</span><br><span class="line">        blabla..</span><br><span class="line">        break</span><br><span class="line">        except NameError:</span><br><span class="line">        blabla..</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li>
</ul>
<h2 id="有趣的库"><a href="#有趣的库" class="headerlink" title="有趣的库"></a>有趣的库</h2><ul>
<li>cowsay（让小牛meow）<br><img src="/img/meow.png" alt="meow"></li>
<li>qrcode<br><img src="/img/custom_qr.png" alt="我的qrcode"></li>
</ul>
<hr>
<h1 id="lecture-7-SQL"><a href="#lecture-7-SQL" class="headerlink" title="lecture 7 SQL"></a>lecture 7 SQL</h1><h2 id="读取csv文件"><a href="#读取csv文件" class="headerlink" title="读取csv文件"></a>读取csv文件</h2><ul>
<li>csv文件 通过逗号分隔值<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">import csv</span><br><span class="line">with open (&quot;favorites.csv,&quot;r&quot;)as file:</span><br><span class="line">       </span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li>
</ul>
<h2 id="sorted"><a href="#sorted" class="headerlink" title="sorted"></a>sorted</h2><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">import csv</span><br><span class="line">with open (&quot;favorites.csv,&quot;r&quot;)as file:</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">       reader=csv.DictReader（file）</span><br><span class="line">       for row in reader：</span><br><span class="line">           print（row[“language”]）</span><br><span class="line">       /* or</span><br><span class="line">       reader=csv.reader(file)</span><br><span class="line">       next(reader)//跳过元数据 描述数据的各列表属性</span><br><span class="line">       */</span><br><span class="line">       cnts=&#123;&#125;</span><br><span class="line">       for row in reader:</span><br><span class="line">        favorites=row[&quot;language&quot;]</span><br><span class="line">        if favorites in cnts:</span><br><span class="line">          cnts[favorites]+=1</span><br><span class="line">        else:</span><br><span class="line">          cnts[favorites]=1</span><br><span class="line">for favorites in sorted(cnts,ket=cnts.get,reverse=True):</span><br><span class="line">    print(f&quot;&#123;favorites&#125;:&#123;cnts[favorites]&#125;&quot;)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h2 id="sql-语法"><a href="#sql-语法" class="headerlink" title="sql 语法"></a>sql 语法</h2><p><strong>CRUD</strong>语法 即：</p>
<ul>
<li>create ：insert</li>
<li>read ：select sth from </li>
<li>update sth set value</li>
<li>delete from sth where condition、 drop</li>
<li>减少冗余</li>
<li>one to many</li>
<li>many to many</li>
</ul>
<h3 id="由-csv-db"><a href="#由-csv-db" class="headerlink" title="由.csv-&gt;.db"></a>由.csv-&gt;.db</h3><p>cs50中用到splite3 但以前用的是Access 没有实践过以下终端命令</p>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">splite3 favorites.db</span><br><span class="line">.mode csv</span><br><span class="line">.import favorites.csv favorites</span><br><span class="line">.quit</span><br><span class="line">之后同时会有csv和db文件</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h3 id="选取表示"><a href="#选取表示" class="headerlink" title="选取表示"></a>选取表示</h3><p><strong>注意用英文模式</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>NULL 表示没有数据</li>
<li>select * from favorites；</li>
<li>select * from favorites limit 10；</li>
<li>AVG COUNT DISTINCT LOWER MAX MIN UPPER</li>
<li>LIMIt 限制输出：<ul>
<li>where </li>
<li>like</li>
<li>order by</li>
<li>limit</li>
<li>group by</li>
<li>join：select * <strong>from</strong> a <strong>join</strong> b <strong>on</strong> a.id&#x3D;b.id</li>
<li><ul>
<li><img src="/img/lecture7.jpg" alt="嵌套语句"></li>
</ul>
</li>
<li>又或者一次性连接多个表<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">SELECT title FROM shows</span><br><span class="line">JOIN stars ON shows.id=stars.show_id</span><br><span class="line">JOIN people ON stars.person_id=people.id;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li>
<li>便利的<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">SELECT title FROM shows,stars,people</span><br><span class="line">WHERE shows.id=stars.show_id</span><br><span class="line">AND people.id=stars.person_id</span><br><span class="line">AND name=&quot;STEVE CARELL&quot;;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
<h2 id="ACCESS思维导图和SQL语句练习题"><a href="#ACCESS思维导图和SQL语句练习题" class="headerlink" title="ACCESS思维导图和SQL语句练习题"></a>ACCESS思维导图和SQL语句练习题</h2>

	<div class="row">
    <embed src="/file/Access.pdf" width="100%" height="550" type="application/pdf">
	</div>






	<div class="row">
    <embed src="/file/sql习题课作业.pdf" width="100%" height="550" type="application/pdf">
	</div>




<p><strong>os</strong>：一下子写完lecture5-10似乎太多，于是决定把8-10的笔记放到另外一篇文章</p>
]]></content>
